{"ec":"ET00058961","t":"Rangasthalam","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/rangasthalam-et00058961-05-11-2020-05-47-22.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/rangasthalam-et00058961-05-11-2020-05-47-22.jpg","d":"A happy-go-lucky Chitti Babu, who has a partial hearing disability, lives in a village called Rangasthalam and is unaffected by the perpetual chaos created in the village by its dreaded president, Garu. However, when his elder brother Kumar Babu returns home from Dubai and finds out that not much had changed around him, he decides to take on Garu. Not letting his disability come his way, Chitti joins his brother in his fight.","rd":"2018-03-30","rt":179,"ct":"UA","g":["Drama","Historical","Romantic"],"l":["Telugu"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Ram Charan","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/ram-charan-teja-1046368-19-09-2017-02-37-43.jpg"],["Samantha Ruth Prabhu","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/samantha-ruth-prabhu-36761-1680672597.jpg"],["Prakash Raj","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/prakash-raj-1713-1752826706.jpg"],["Aadhi","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/aadhi-pinisetty-13992-18-09-2017-03-39-03.jpg"],["Anasuya Bharadwaj","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/anasuya-bharadwaj-1065308-1722674916.jpg"],["Jagapati Babu","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/jagapati-babu-5809-1720595411.jpg"],["Amit Sharma","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/amit-sharma-iein114897-21-08-2017-18-22-09.jpg"],["Pooja Hegde","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/pooja-hegde-30494-1780580709.jpg"]],"crew":{"d":[["Sukumar Bandreddi","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/sukumar-bandreddi-227