{"ec":"ET00027881","t":"Nanak Shah Fakir","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/nanak-shah-fakir-et00027881-01-04-2018-12-49-32.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/nanak-shah-fakir-et00027881-01-04-2018-12-49-32.jpg","d":"The film is based on the life and teachings of Guru Nanak Dev Ji. Born in 1469, Nanak traveled the world to spread the essence of `Ik Onkar` (there is but One God) as a philosophy and way of life. A philosophy that has survived and risen above the flux of conflict and time, impacting over 50 million followers worldwide and giving birth to Sikhsm as a way of life. <br/><br/>Throughout his life, Guru Nanak shared his blessings of divine knowledge through mystic and soulfully divine music. He sang to the Lord and taught us, ordinary mortals, the virtues of peace, love and harmony. Guru Nanak was referred to as Shah by the Muslims and Fakir by the Hindus, the highest honor given in both religions, and hence came to be known as Nanak Shah Fakir.","rd":"2018-04-13","rt":145,"ct":"UA","g":["Biography","Devotional","Drama"],"l":["Hindi","Punjabi"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Arif Zakaria","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/arif-zakaria-13551-23-03-2021-01-00-28.jpg"],["Puneet Sikka","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/puneet-sikka-25856-12-04-2018-11-44-29.jpg"],["Shraddha Kaul","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/shraddha-kaul-21350-1765724457.jpg"],["Anurag Arora","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/anurag-arora-32142-11-04-2017-15-42-22.jpg"],["Adil Hussain","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/adil-hussain-30788-05-05-2017-11-34-46.jpg"],["Narendra Jha","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/narendra-jha-1553-19-12-2018-02-26-05.jpg"]],"crew":{"d":[["Sartaj Singh Pannu","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/sartaj-singh-pannu-16989-24-03-2017-14-12-39.jpg"]],"p":[],"m":[["Uttam Singh","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/uttam-singh-4945-12-02-2018-12-17-51.jpg"]],"c":[],"e":[]}}
{"ec":"ET00073719","t":"Chalbaaz","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/chalbaaz-et00073719-06-04-2018-03-12-49.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/chalbaaz-et00073719-06-04-2018-03-12-49.jpg","d":"A young guy named Raja moves to the UK to make it big. There he meets Srijata who eloped with her long-time boyfriend. As time passes by, her boyfriend cheats and leaves her stranded. The chain of events goes unpredictably when Srijata requests Raja to come along with her to Kolkata and help her clear the mess that occurred due to her elopement. How does Raja tackle the whole situation is what the movie is all about.","rd":"2018-04-20","rt":159,"ct":"UA","g":["Comedy","Romantic"],"l":["Bengali"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Shakib Khan","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/shakib-khan-1073004-10-01-2018-03-31-28.jpg"],["Subhasree Ganguly","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/subhasree-ganguly-1045490-09-08-2017-18-29-37.jpg"],["Ashish Vidyarthi","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/ashish-vidyarthi-3400-27-08-2020-02-59-37.jpg"],["Rajatabha Dutta","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/rajatabha-dutta-iein108523-25-04-2017-15-02-29.jpg"],["Kharaj Mukherjee","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/kharaj-mukherjee-16716-1659083642.jpg"],["Sagnik","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/sagnik-1048348-27-07-2017-18-50-54.jpg"],["Joydeep Mukherjee","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/joydeep-mukherjee-37003-02-12-2021-01-36-35.jpg"]],"crew":{"d":[["Joydeep Mukherjee","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/joydeep-mukherjee-37003-02-12-2021-01-36-35.jpg"]],"p":[["Ashok Dhanuka","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster